{"tid":54722,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高登 vs 連登 大比拚!!! version 1.0","createTime":"2016-12-25T18:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T11:01:03.000Z","uid":12034,"like":14,"dislike":124,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17bb189e5de6f14b67e8c82f5ba002fc4610e39b","tid":54722,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:44:16.000Z","msg":"高登<br />\n<br />\n上線人數 🔴🔴⚪️⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n會員質素 🔴🔴🔴⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n帖文質素 🔴🔴🔴⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n管理質素 🔴🔴🔴🔴⚪️<br />\n<br />\nios 評分  🔴⚪️⚪️⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\nan 評分   🔴🔴🔴🔴🔴<br />\n<br />\n網頁評分 🔴🔴🔴🔴🔴<br />\n<br />\n附屬功能 🔴🔴🔴⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥力 : 26🔴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登<br />\n<br />\n上線人數 🔵🔵🔵⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n會員質素 🔵🔵⚪️⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n帖文質素 🔵🔵🔵⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n管理質素 🔵⚪️⚪️⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\nios 評分  🔵🔵🔵🔵⚪️<br />\n<br />\nan 評分   🔵🔵🔵🔵⚪️<br />\n<br />\n網頁評分 🔵⚪️⚪️⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n附屬功能 🔵🔵⚪️⚪️⚪️<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥力 : 20🔵<br />\n<br />\n結論 : <br />\n<br />\n連登完敗，主要原因 : <br />\n肥婆icon一事拖累論壇質素，管理水平敗露；<br />\n幾乎任意注冊，各區打手密佈；<br />\n未有贊助版本以致廣告不停出現；<br />\n網頁測試版大學生功課水平<br />\n<br />\n高登稍勝原因：<br />\n早信團隊知錯能改，an版m版飛躍改善；<br />\n連登內亂，人流回歸高登<br />\n<br />\n估計高登ios app上架後<br />\nversion 2.0時 高登將會拋離連登10分<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"622cb568ce6384cef6af39144f77ce39a6e810a0","tid":54722,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:45:34.000Z","msg":"Ching Ho ball"},{"pid":"761984022d5ec210f2049e700470997e99224aec","tid":54722,"uid":43370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"冇人會返高登"},{"pid":"331cfaf4beaffa892164f854821e8ffc07f09f61","tid":54722,"uid":9492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:49:46.000Z","msg":"高登網頁評分有5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eab15c23a7775c0e49e00311221c44af0eef06f","tid":54722,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"我信你曲線"},{"pid":"8cdebc638761278283fd24f0f2ee6f